{
  "name": "stm32f103c6t6_golden_with_uart_roundtrip",
  "description": "Opt-in STM32F103C6T6 extended golden suite on the ESP32JTAG STM32 bench for the cross-instrument UART wiring mode. This pack keeps the canonical staged suite but replaces the three DUT-local UART tests with one cross-instrument UART roundtrip proof through the ESP32JTAG Port B web UART bridge. That roundtrip proof is intentionally promoted into pre-Stage2 connectivity so the wrong UART wiring mode fails early instead of late in Stage 2. Use it only when the extra UART wiring is present: STM32 PA9 to ESP32JTAG UART RX, ESP32JTAG UART TX to STM32 PA10, plus common ground. It also requires ESP32JTAG firmware with the UART pin fix at or after commit 9a1610f.",
